Tomarrow is my birthday party! i can not wait.  tonight i am going to a birthday party in Woonsocket with my cousin Bri.  i'm excited but i don't know if its going to be fun because i really only know my cousin.  i am also sleeping over than when i go home on saturday i have to get ready for people to come over at like 2 than i have three people sleeping over. it is going to be so much fun.  on sunday i am going to probly sit around all day and rest after my friends go home. maybe i will go shopping.  on monday MY BIRTHDAY i am going to sleep really late because i will probly not get any sleep all weekend.  i have to study really hard because of exams on tuesday and i have to study for my permit test.  i am going to get my permit on tuesday and i have my two hardest exams, english and history.  my mom is going to pick me up at 11:40 and then we are going out to lunch and then she is going to bring me to get my permit.  after that she is going to bring me to drive around in a parking lot because i have never driven behind the wheel ever in my life. i am so excited. this weekend is going to be the best party weekend but it also sucks because i have to study for my exams and i really am dreading them.

I'm so excited my birthday is in 10 days and i will get my permit in 11 days.  I can't wait!! My back hurts so bad from shoveling snow yesterday.  rrrrr. then i had to go and do chores.  well i have no clue what to say.  ooo yea my computer is broken, it won't even start. rrrrrr. well bye
